OL,7,FA teenager googled "how many years in
OL,8,Fjail for attempted murder?" after his
OL,9,Ffriend attacked an innocent 14-year-
OL,10,Fold boy with a machete.
OL,12,FDeclan Pendlebury, now 21, has been
OL,13,Fsentenced to 19 years in prison at
OL,14,FLiverpool Crown Court on Monday 8
OL,15,FDecember for the attempted murder of a
OL,16,Fboy in St Helens.
OL,18,FMerseyside Police are also appealing
OL,19,Ffor a second man, Robin Singh, in
OL,20,Fconnection with the attack.
