OL,7,FPendlebury and Singh had reportedly
OL,8,Flooked for potential targets from a
OL,9,F"rival area" in a park before
OL,10,Fattacking a victim who had been
OL,11,Fplaying football with his brother and
OL,12,Ffriends.
OL,14,FLiverpool Crown Court heard that
OL,15,FPendlebury took a taxi to Singh's home
OL,16,Fon Fairclough Street in Burtonwood,
OL,17,FWarrington, at around 6pm on 2
OL,18,FSeptember 2024.
