OL,7,FThe two teenagers then left in an Uber
OL,8,Fshortly before 10pm, wearing
OL,9,Fbalaclavas and a change of clothing.
OL,11,FWilliam Beardmore, prosecuting,
OL,12,Fdescribed how they were dropped in the
OL,13,Farea of Gaskell Park in St Helens
OL,14,Fbefore encountering the 14-year-old,
OL,15,Fhis older brother and a group of their
OL,16,Ffriends on Pennine Drive.
OL,18,FSingh, whose whereabouts are currently
OL,19,Funknown, shouted: "Are you from the
OL,20,F9s?", in an apparent reference to the
OL,21,FWA9 postcode area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
