OL,7,FThe then 17-year-old, now aged 19,
OL,8,Fthen produced a large machete and ran
OL,9,Fat the group, before attacking the
OL,10,Fvictim.
OL,12,FSingh reportedly went on to
OL,13,F"repeatedly stab and slash" at him in
OL,14,Fwhat was described as a "frenzied
OL,15,Fattack," as Pendlebury was "at his
OL,16,Fside throughout."
