OL,7,FThe injured teen was left with a
OL,8,F"significant wound" to his left knee
OL,9,Ffollowing the assault, also suffering
OL,10,Fthe partial amputation of one of his
OL,11,Ftoes.
OL,13,FPendlebury and Singh fled the scene.
OL,15,FSingh was seen to deposit a black bag
OL,16,Fat the rear of his house shortly
OL,17,Fbefore midnight, which was later
OL,18,Frecovered by police. It contained the
OL,19,Fclothes that the two were wearing
OL,20,Fduring the attack.
