OL,9,Fhimself in at St Helens Police Station.
OL,11,FThe phone which he began using the
OL,12,Ffollowing day had been used to conduct
OL,13,Fonline searches for "how many years in
OL,14,Fjail for attempted murder?" and view
OL,15,Fnews articles relating to the incident.
