OL,7,FAppearing via video link to HMP
OL,8,FLiverpool on Monday 8 September, he
OL,9,Fshowed no reaction as he was handed 19
OL,10,Fyears in a young offenders' institute
OL,11,Fand an indefinite restraining order.
OL,13,FSentencing, the Honorary Recorder of
OL,14,FLiverpool Judge Andrew Menary KC said:
OL,15,F"This was a grave offence, committed
OL,16,Fagainst a 14-year-old child who was
OL,17,Fentirely innocent of any wrongdoing
OL,18,Fand unconnected to you or your co-
OL,19,Faccused Robin Smith, who has absconded
OL,20,Fand remains at large.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
